Interface Inactivatable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Concept, Description
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConceptImpl, DescriptionImpl, InactivatableImpl

    public interface Inactivatable
extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject
    Representation of all SNOMED CT components that could be retired. In other word the component could be inactivated.
    For more details, please refer to Component.isActive().

    The following features are supported:

    • Inactivation Indicator Ref Set Members
    • Association Ref Set Members

    See Also:
    SnomedPackage.getInactivatable()
